column2: Elder Dragons and Star Navigation Theories Vol. III
Activate the Soul Battery Fragment before defeating the Legendary Risen High Wizard at the Narthex in Cursed Shore to capture its soul energy.
Created by ore synthesizers in Lost Precipice. Used to craft guild weapons and armor.

Created by ore synthesizers in Gilded Hollow. Used to craft guild weapons and armor.
<c=@flavor>An empty notebook for containing your notes on hylek alchemy.<c>
<c=@flavor>A talisman from Sabetha's stores that resonates with ancient power.</c>
Speak with Jett, along the southern road exiting Griffonfall in Auric Basin, to obtain the M-PEC.

Take the Charged Dwarven Spell Trap, Energized Soul Battery Fragment, Case of Corrupted Phials, and Chaotic Magic to the Metal Forest on Pyrite Peninsula in Malchor's Leap to combine them into Transcendent Energy.
Activate the M-PEC before defeating a Champion Stonehead near the Griffonfall Pylon in Auric Basin to gather its salivary stone.
Activate the M-PEC before defeating the Veteran Follower of Zintl outside the Capitzel Grounds in Auric Basin to gather their beetle's juice.
Purchased from Rebel Isaak in Frostgorge Sound.
Corrupt a Pure Crystalline Phial in your inventory by defeating a Veteran Branded Spark found east of Skara Braevus in Blazeridge Steppes.
Used in the crafting of armor with +Power, +Vitality, +Concentration, and +Toughness.
Activate the M-PEC before defeating a Champion Mushroom Emperor in Tangled Depths, Auric Basin, or Dragon's Stand to gather its spores.

To complete the Catalytic Converter, combine the jungle dragon cores with the Incomplete Catalytic Converter and a Vision Crystal by channeling the Ancient Power Core inside the secret lab beneath the Decayed Hive in Tangled Depths.
A volatile ingredient looted from Vilnia Shadowsong near the Raven Shaman's Power Source hidden within Darkhoof Heights in Snowden Drifts.

Take the Sextant, Astrolabe, Incomplete Star Charts, and Star Charter's Bag along with Ogden's Notes to the Durmand Priory, and use the Cartographer's Workbench to create the Celestial Cartographer's Gear.
Raid entrances are marked with a red portal. Travel to an entrance and speak with the informant to learn more. Check your map to find all the available raids.
Used in the crafting of weapons with +Expertise and +Vitality.
If you can't stand the heat...
The Keep Construct is attracting energy to unleash Magic Blast.

+5%% damage against monsters. 
<c=@reminder>Will be removed if you enter competitive PvP or a raid.</c>
With an Empty Hylek Flask in your inventory, mix the six jungle bacteria to create the Concentrated Maguuma Bacteria.

Infuse Spirit Threads from Gorseval the Multifarious in Spirit Vale with ley-line energy released when defeating a chak gerent near the Ley-Line Confluence in the Tangled Depths. Combine 5 Energized Spirit Threads to create a Spirit Weave.
After learning the special technique, defeat the Canyon Spider Queen located inside the Sweltering Canyons of Fireheart Rise and loot her venom.
You have found a ley rift. Train the Rift Forger Mastery in Forsaken Thicket to use it to repair your armor.
Used in the crafting of weapons with +Power, +Vitality, +Concentration, and +Toughness.
Used in the crafting of weapons with +Expertise and +Vitality.
Allows the collection of Elemental Flames.
Speak with Ogden, in the Durmand Priory within Lornar's Pass, to obtain this.
Note: Glider Basics and Updraft Use Masteries are required to successfully complete some encounters.
Follow the third player on the blue team.
Activate the Soul Battery Fragment before defeating the Champion Risen Knight, located near the Dwayna Statue in Malchor's Leap, to capture its soul energy.
Enter the Forsaken Thicket in Verdant Brink and defeat a boss to unlock.
Follow the fourth player on the blue team.
With an Empty Hylek Flask in your inventory, mix the four volatile ingredients to form the Concentrated Volatile Substance.
Used in the crafting of armor with +Power, +Vitality, +Concentration, and +Toughness.
Used in the crafting of weapons with +Toughness, +Healing, +Concentration, and +Vitality.
Complete this book by recording the three Hylek Alchemy Chapters in your Hylek Alchemy Apprentice Tome by passing each of Atlalli's tests with the tome in your inventory.
Used in the crafting of weapons with +Condition Damage, +Power, +Expertise, and +Precision.
You can now bathe in the healing Forsaken Thicket waters and cleanse your afflictions.
Players who are ready when the game begins earn %num1% rank points.
Used in the crafting of armor with +Condition Damage, +Power, +Expertise, and +Precision.
Used in the crafting of armor with +Power, +Toughness, +Concentration, and +Expertise.
Used to reduce build times at the workshop. This guild receives 100 resonance upon purchase.
Used in the crafting of armor with +Toughness, +Healing Power, and +Concentration.
After learning the special technique, defeat the Legendary Chak Gerent in Tangled Depths to gather its ichor.
Follow the first player on the red team.
Allows the collection of Wyvern Liquid Fire.
Speak with Atlalli, the Mastery Alchemist at the Hunting Grounds in Timberline Falls, to learn his secret ichor extraction technique.
With the Crystallized Magic in your inventory, gather chaotic ley-line energy by defeating earth elementals near Omadd's Machine within the Cavern of the Shining Lights in Dry Top.
Unlocks recipes for Aurillium Capsules, Quartz Vials, Obsidian Magma Containers, and Mist-Imbued Jars.
Used in the crafting of armor with +Toughness, +Condition Damage, +Expertise, and +Vitality.
With the Crystallized Magic in your inventory, gather the searing's chaotic energy by looting the chest at the end of the Urban Battlegrounds Fractal.

Usable by any character, this pack comes with everything you need to celebrate winter in style.

Appearance skins override the look of your equipment and have no stats of their own.
<c=@flavor>This tube is created from alchemical reactants and provides a violent reaction when mixed correctly with Transcendent Energy.<c>

Increase movement speed by 15%%.

Activate the M-PEC before defeating a Champion Arrowhead at Arrowhead Vale in Auric Basin to gather its mucus.
Used in the crafting of armor with +Toughness, +Healing, +Concentration, and +Vitality.
Combine with 20 Vials of Powerful Blood, 50 Vials of Potent Blood, and 250 Piles of Bloodstone Dust in the Mystic Forge to create a Mystic Essence of Determination.
Toggles the visibility of the squad broadcast chat panel.
A recipe to make an ascended inscription for crafting weapons with Commander's (+Power, +Precision, +Toughness, and +Concentration) stats.
After learning the special technique, defeat the Champion Wasp Queen near the Ebonhawke Delegation in Fields of Ruin to gather her ichor.
Corrupt a Pure Crystalline Phial in your inventory by defeating Vinetooth Prime inside Vinetooth's Den in Auric Basin.
A Pact representative is standing guard outside the Forsaken Thicket, just north of Batrach Falls. He should have more information regarding the situation.
